</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>ID</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The tag ID is automatically assigned and cannot be changed.
It is used to uniquely identify your tags.</p>
<p class="tableblock"><strong><em>Use case</em></strong>: Tag links can be imported.
For example, while you import item and variation data, you can also directly link the appropriate tags.
This is done, e.g. by specifying the tag ID.</p></td>
