<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Name EN</strong><br>
<span class="red">(Mandatory field)</span></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter a name for the tag.
