<p class="tableblock"><strong><em>Tip</em></strong>: The name can include spaces. As such, tag names can consist of multiple words.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Colour</strong></p></td>
