</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Board</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Do you want to highlight specific task cards on boards?<br>
<strong><em>Example:</em></strong> Specify that some tasks have a high or low priority.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Category Link</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Do you want to highlight specific categories in the back end?<br>
<strong><em>Example:</em></strong> Specify that a category should only be used for seasonal offers.</p>
<p class="tableblock"><strong><em>Note</em></strong>: Category tags are <em>not visible</em> to customers in the online store.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
