</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Order</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Do you want to highlight specific reorders and redistributions?<br>
<strong><em>Example</em></strong>: Specify which kind of products were reordered or redistributed.</p>
<p class="tableblock"><strong><em>Note</em></strong>: Currently, tags can only be used for reorders and redistributions. They cannot be used for any other order types.</p></td>
