</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Currency</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The system currency is displayed in this field by default. If needed, enter a different <strong>Currency</strong> for the supplier as well as the <strong>Exchange rate</strong> that is currently valid for the currency. The <strong>Details</strong> area will then include a display of the calculated <strong>Net order value</strong>.</p></td>
