<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">The amount is set to 0 by default. Enter the amount of the respective cost in the currency it is charged in for this reorder.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Currency</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the currency in which the amount for this cost is charged.</p></td>
